{"tid":2141991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭蟲太：熱血公民是全港第一個政黨在街上派口罩","createTime":"2020-08-06T05:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T21:00:09.000Z","uid":312744,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"538909d30d50d7c969ba962acdf27123b7926b06","tid":2141991,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"在瘟疫政治下，香港已經成為「以口罩入罪」、「以口罩取人」的地方，但大眾未有察覺當中的問題所在，甚至有人要求趕走、捕捉街市內的貓隻以防播毒，學習大陸的做法。<br />\n<br />\n在一個人人瘋狂的時代，保持平常心，冷靜理智地防疫，除了合理地戴口罩外，最緊要的是勤洗手、勤洗手、勤洗手。<br />\n<br />\n註：小弟戴的不是KF94，是某個 Made in Hong Kong 的牌子，比較厚身，長戴會有點焗呢。另外在疫症初期，熱血公民是全港第一個政黨在街上派口罩，並呼籲大家注重衛生的。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQggg8C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQggg8C.png&h=aa3a0504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝熱血公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d2e32397adf08e7ed948559a43fd348d662640","tid":2141991,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"乜水黎<br />\n個個post都見到佢"},{"pid":"f9b595fca81e30ef33a6573006ef70b2f8bf0251","tid":2141991,"uid":140924,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"咁你個黨又屌人哋係口罩法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：當年投咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2aa5df7fe7804da08f47b65d67d34a7a677956","tid":2141991,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"香港有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a312e22f93c7de4140f9d25892cd169e2585f2","tid":2141991,"uid":103230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large